because the worship
of Me is no more upon him.

38:02.864 --> 38:06.533
So take you his life
and spill his blood."

38:06.618 --> 38:08.869
- He did?
- Yeah.

38:08.954 --> 38:12.206
"But let not the flesh
pollute the corn.

