Make sacrifice unto Him.

39:00.130 --> 39:03.298
Bring Him the blood
of the outIanders.

39:03.383 --> 39:05.718
( all chanting )
Praise God! Praise the Lord!

39:05.802 --> 39:08.512
Praise God!
Praise the Lord!

39:08.596 --> 39:11.432
Praise God! Praise the Lord!

39:11.516 --> 39:14.101
Praise God!
Praise the Lord!

39:14.185 --> 39:16.770
Praise God! Praise the Lord!

