Oh my God!

59:06.251 --> 59:08.419
( bell tolling )

59:10.756 --> 59:13.549
( roaring )

59:22.559 --> 59:26.145
( crowd cheering )

59:38.408 --> 59:41.327
( screams )

59:43.413 --> 59:46.457
( crowd chanting )
KiII kiII kiII kiII...

